big to be human.

94
00:04:43,116 --> 00:04:44,826
Well, send down a few kids.
That should dislodge it.

95
00:04:44,909 --> 00:04:46,202
MAN (on radio):
<i>Keep 'em coming, Biff.</i>

96
00:04:46,286 --> 00:04:47,745
Roger.

97
00:04:47,829 --> 00:04:49,372
(kids laughing)

98
