116
00:05:34,125 --> 00:05:36,294
Don't pull any punches.

117
00:05:36,377 --> 00:05:38,880
Am I just a little bit
overweight?

118
00:05:41,049 --> 00:05:43,634
-Well, am I?
-Forgive us, Dad,

119
00:05:43,718 --> 00:05:45,970
